name: Create Omnisend custom events from new Google Sheets rows
description: Every time a new row is added to your Google Sheets spreadsheet, Make will automatically create a new custom events in Omnisend. The template uses this [example spreadsheet](https://docs.google.com/spreadsheets/d/1A5KVRtkA-B3gAGnjQycXXgvMbATMoWXlcP9bJqfAvzo/edit?usp=sharing).
